Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.64,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm not here to see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.64,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,見送りじゃなくて 悪かったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.96,Default,av,0,0,0,,We both have jobs to do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.96,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お互い仕事だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:03.24,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Lawless Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:03.24,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,Lawless Heavenか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.21,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.76,Default,tig,0,0,0,,You'd make a fortune selling that in Chicago!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.76,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,こいつはシカゴで売りゃ ぼろ儲けだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.22,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,コルテはいい奴だった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:16.52,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Corteo was a nice guy. Fango probably fed him a line or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.52,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,きっとファンゴの野郎に騙されたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:21.14,Default,tig,0,0,0,,But we still gotta finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:21.14,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,だが ケジメはつけなきゃならねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:25.61,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.01,Default,av,0,0,0,,May I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.01,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,行ってもいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:30.90,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.44,Default,av,0,0,0,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.44,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なかなか似合ってるね
