Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Corteo didn't show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.78,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,コルテオは現れなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.46,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Yeah, Avilio set off for Chicago alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.46,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,うん アヴィリオは一人でシカゴに向かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's not in on it. How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.43,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,彼奴は無関係だ 何度言ったら分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.81,Default,av,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.81,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんただったんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.85,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Right answer, Angelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.85,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,正解だ アンジェロ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.17,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why did you send me that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.17,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何故俺に手紙をよこした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.79,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Vincent kept worrying over Testa's son that got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.79,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントは逃げたテスタの息子を気に病んでいてな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:18.42,Default,gan,0,0,0,,He told me to track you down by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:18.42,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,どんな手を使ってでも お前を探しだすよう頼まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.80,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.80,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.24,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You're dead, as far as he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.24,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,お前はもう死んた事になってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.92,Default,gan,0,0,0,,To be honest, my hopes\N weren't high, but you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.92,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,正直 大して期待してなかったが上出来だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.86,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,少しヘマしたみたいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:36.40,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You made a few blunders along the way, but the way you killed Vanno had style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.40,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,バンノンの殺しっぷりもいかしてたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.31,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why do you want the Vanettis dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.31,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんたは何故バネッチィの奴らを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.38,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Good liquor, good women,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.38,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,旨い酒にいい女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:49.26,Default,gan,0,0,0,,and the town of Lawless, all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:49.26,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,それにローレスの町 すべてを手に入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.19,Default,gan,0,0,0,,It's any man's fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.19,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,男のロマンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.14,Default,av,0,0,0,,You killed Nero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.14,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロはやったんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,I can kill Nero any time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.20,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロはいつでもやれる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.36,Default,av,0,0,0,,but Vincent won't go down that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.36,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,でも ヴィンセントはそうは行かない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:05.27,Default,av,0,0,0,,To kill Vincent, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:05.27,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ヴィンセントを殺すためには あんたが必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,You need me as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.20,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんたも俺が必要なんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.82,Default,av,0,0,0,,Let me have Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.82,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオを渡してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.55,Default,av,0,0,0,,Once he's safe, I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.55,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,逃がしたら戻ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.71,Default,gan,0,0,0,,And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.71,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,嫌だっと言ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.68,Default,av,0,0,0,,I've entrusted the letter to a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.68,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,手紙をある男に預けた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.08,Default,av,0,0,0,,It gets sent to Nero if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.08,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺が死ねば ネロのもとに届く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,With the name of the man who really sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.24,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,本当の差し出し人の名前を添えてなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:44.09,Default,gan,0,0,0,,For now, you should pick a familiar place to lay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:44.09,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,とりあえず 落ち着く先は馴染みの場所がいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.50,Default,woman,0,0,0,,They have the best prices there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.50,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,あの店やすいんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.96,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.96,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,あら そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.47,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Mr. Bruno! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.47,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,ブルノさん どこに行ってたんだい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.89,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Hey, you owe me back rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:03.34,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,ちょっと 家賃溜まってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.53,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Excuse me, will this cover it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.53,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,あの これで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.10,Default,woman,0,0,0,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.10,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,これじゃ多すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.64,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Take it as an advance on future rent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.64,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,この先の分も ここから取ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.60,Default,woman,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.88,Default,woman,0,0,0,,There's so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.88,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,こんなに...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.24,Default,cor,0,0,0,,It's quite spartan, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.24,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,随分質素だね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.07,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.18,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'll sleep here for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.18,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,今日は僕がここに寝るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.45,Default,cor,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.45,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,これは...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.66,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,この部屋に居た時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.44,Default,av,0,0,0,,When I lived in this room I was an empty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.44,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺は抜け殻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.43,Default,av,0,0,0,,Until that letter came...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.43,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あの手紙が届くまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.69,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.69,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.58,Default,av,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,You slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.09,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,よく寝ってだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:26.07,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I hadn't been sleeping much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:26.07,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ここんところ あまり寝てなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.18,Default,av,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.18,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,飲むだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,This is the only cup I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.13,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,カップ これしかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.48,Default,cor,0,0,0,,So sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.48,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,甘っ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You always did love sweet stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,昔から 甘いものが好きだったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.85,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I need to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.85,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,買い物に行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.95,Default,av,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.95,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何を買うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.41,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Blankets, utensils...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.41,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,毛布とか 食器とか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.20,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,後 せっかく来たんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:59.29,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Oh, and as long as I'm here, why not\N take me to some of your favorite places?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.29,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,お気に入りの場所とかも連れてってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.96,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.96,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.89,Default,av,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Mr. Strega.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.89,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ストレーガさんによろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.26,Default,av,0,0,0,,Corteo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.26,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.88,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You're going back to Lawless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.88,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ローレスに戻るんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.70,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll stop by Chicago, then head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.70,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あぁ シカゴに寄って そのまま戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.70,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You'll come back here, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.70,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,帰ってくるよね ここに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.42,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.33,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.33,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,帰ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:53.91,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:53.91,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.33,Default,vin,0,0,0,,How's the playhouse coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.33,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,劇場の方は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Right on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.79,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,順調だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The orchestra we've got rehearsing\N is saying good things about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.28,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,リハーサルに入ってる楽団からも評判がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.46,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.46,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.82,Default,vin,0,0,0,,It's been a long road,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.82,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,色々あったが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.18,Default,vin,0,0,0,,but if we can patch up our\N relationship with the Galassias,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.18,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ガラッシアとの関係がしっかりすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.37,Default,vin,0,0,0,,that should clear up the last of our worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.37,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,とりあえず憂いはなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.86,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you can't beat 'em, join 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.86,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あぁ 長いものには巻かれろってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.93,Default,vin,0,0,0,,What they want is to expand steadily,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.93,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,奴らが望んでいるのは着実な発展だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.21,Default,vin,0,0,0,,not to destroy and conquer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.21,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,破壊と征服じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.36,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,礼を尽くして付き合う限り
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.89,Default,vin,0,0,0,,As long as we're courteous, they'll be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.89,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,無茶はしないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Won't let us live, but won't kill us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.34,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,生かさず殺さず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,その上で 俺達から上前を撥ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:06.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,They'll just hang over us at all times, taking kickbacks and growing fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.94,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ブクブク太っていく訳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.94,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.94,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,お前の気持ちも分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.32,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,だがな ガラッシアその気になれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.63,Default,vin,0,0,0,,but in as little as a month, if they wanted to they could...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.70,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ほんの一ヶ月で...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.09,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.09,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,安心しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:19.22,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm not so stupid as to try something right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:19.22,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今すぐどうこうしようって程バカじゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Think carefully, then walk forward with purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:24.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,よく考えろ そしてゆっくりと歩め
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The faster you rush, the more likely you are to trip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:28.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,速く走ろうとする者ほど 転びやすいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.68,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.68,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.57,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.57,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,オヤジ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'll protect the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺は何があっても ファミリーを守り通して見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.42,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Jeez, we can't find that guy anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.42,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ったく どこ探しても見つかんねぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.40,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,コルテオもそうだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.69,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about Corteo... but about Avilio, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.69,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アヴィリオが気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:47.34,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He called us from Chicago, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:47.34,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,でも シカゴから連絡があったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.41,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He said the deal went great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.41,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,取引は上手くいったって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.55,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The Galassias corroborated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.55,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ガラッシアからの裏も取れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.90,Default,bar,0,0,0,,He's been gone a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.90,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,やつがここを発ってから一週間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.80,Default,bar,0,0,0,,If he'd gone straight to Chicago, it'd have only taken a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.80,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,まっすく向かえばシカゴまで 丸一日あれば行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.62,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Come on, it's his big trip to Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.62,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,おいおい せっかくシカゴに行ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.55,Default,tig,0,0,0,,What's wrong with spending a few days living the high life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.55,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,二三日遊んだって別に悪くねだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.95,Default,tig,0,0,0,,The women they've got there ain't like the ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.95,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,女だって こっちのと浮気が違うだろうしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.41,Default,gan,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.41,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.64,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,昔シカゴの女を抱いた時は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:14.51,Default,gan,0,0,0,,The woman I took to bed in Chicago \Nleft me limp for a week. Sickly, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.51,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,一週間骨抜きされて病気まで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.93,Default,av,0,0,0,,What are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.93,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なんの相談だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.04,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Avilio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.04,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.02,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey, want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.02,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,や なんか飲むか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.15,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sounds like business went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.15,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,商売は上手くいったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.31,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got almost everything we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.31,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あぁ こっちの言い分は大体通った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.47,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It took you quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.47,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,随分遅かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:31.83,Default,av,0,0,0,,There was a lot in Chicago that I had to try out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:31.83,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,シカゴじゃ 色々試さなきゃならなかったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.64,Default,tig,0,0,0,,See? What'd I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.64,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ほらな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.58,Default,tig,0,0,0,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.58,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,で どうだったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.99,Default,tig,0,0,0,,They got good stuff over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.99,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,向こうの上物は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.49,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.49,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,大したことないな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.49,Default,av,0,0,0,,The quality of the alcohol was poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.49,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,アルコールの質も低い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.92,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,カクテルにして誤魔化すならとまかく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:46.05,Default,av,0,0,0,,They can mix it in cocktails to hide it, but the straight stuff is crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.05,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そのままじゃ話にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.67,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Huh?! You were talking about booze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.67,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,酒の話かよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.81,Default,av,0,0,0,,There's no booze in Chicago\N that can top Lawless Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:51.81,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ローレスヘブンに勝る酒はシカゴにはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:55.76,Default,av,0,0,0,,Don Galassia and his underboss, Strega, both agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:55.76,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ドン ガラッシアとアンダーボスのストレーガも認めていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.60,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Honest to a fault, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.60,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,バカ正直な野郎だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,とりあえず 一杯やろうぜい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:04.49,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Avilio, tell us some stories from your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:04.49,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ 土産話でも聞かせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.52,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.52,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,よく戻ってきたな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.62,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You had me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.62,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ひやひやしたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:21.86,花語製作通用-ja,,0,0,0,,本字幕由✿花語&千夏字幕組✿共同製作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.00,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,このままコルテオと仲良く逃避行でもされたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:21.87,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I was afraid you might run off with \NCorteo, and then where would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.87,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,どうしようかと思ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.33,Default,av,0,0,0,,My revenge isn't finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.33,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,復讐はまだ終わってない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.33,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.33,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,その言葉が聞けて安心した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.78,Default,gan,0,0,0,,The playhouse's big opening is in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.78,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,劇場のこけら落としは三日後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.55,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Vincent will be leaving his\N mansion for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.55,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,久しぶりにヴィンセントが屋敷を出る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.48,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You'd better keep him safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.48,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,しっかり守るんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.65,Default,gan,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.65,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.20,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.20,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.78,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.78,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.23,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Use it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.23,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,大事に使え
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.69,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Can't believe it's just two days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.69,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いよいよ明後日か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.76,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Don Galassia will come, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.76,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,予定通りドンガラッシアも来る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.34,Default,gan,0,0,0,,That means he officially\N accepts the Vanettis as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.34,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ヴァネッティを正式に身内と認めたってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.67,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Nero, this town is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.67,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ネロ この町はお前のもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まだ早い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There are still those with lingering loyalty to Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.98,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴの残党は未練たらたらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.55,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There's also Corteo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.55,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そして コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.60,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,お前とヴィンセントは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:32.68,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You and Vincent will need the best security you can get to protect the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.68,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,万全の態勢でゲストを警護しなきゃならん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.97,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Just leave all that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.97,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,その辺の手配は任せておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:35.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Where's Barbero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.85,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,バルベロはどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.26,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He said he was meeting someone at the pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.26,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,なんか 波止場で人と会うとか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.54,Default,bar,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.54,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,その男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.46,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Did he look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.46,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,こんなだった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.64,Default,man,0,0,0,,Dunno. Can't seem to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.64,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,さーな 思い出せね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.74,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Can you come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.74,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,今から来れるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.12,Default,tig,0,0,0,,We've got a lead about Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.12,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,コルテオのことで動きがあった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:14.96,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.48,Default,jon,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I need to search you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.48,通用720日文-ja,jon,0,0,0,,悪いけど 調べさせてもらうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,You found out where Corteo's hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオの居場所が分かったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.41,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.41,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.42,Default,bar,0,0,0,,You let Corteo escape, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.42,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,お前がコルテオを逃がしたか?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:58.18,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,お前がシカゴに経った日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:16:00.23,Default,bar,0,0,0,,The day you left for Chicago, Corteo was at the pier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.23,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,コルテオは波止場にいた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.10,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Isn't that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.10,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.07,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Answer me, Avilio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.07,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,答えよ アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.81,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Someone there saw Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.81,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,コルテオを見たものがいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:09.85,Default,bar,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:09.85,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.72,Default,jon,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.72,通用720日文-ja,jon,0,0,0,,それが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.90,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Save it for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.90,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,後にしろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.87,Default,jon,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.87,通用720日文-ja,jon,0,0,0,,ちょっと待て おい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.31,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.31,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.65,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Mr. Bruno's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.65,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,あんた ブルーノさんの友達かい?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.83,Default,woman,0,0,0,,You'd better stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.83,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,あの子には近づかないほうがいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.46,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.46,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.51,Default,woman,0,0,0,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.51,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,なぜって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:17.00,Default,woman,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a proper job, yet he has all that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:17.00,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,真面に働いてもないのに お金持ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.18,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Listen, take my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.18,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,悪いことは言わないからさあ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.10,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Just stay away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.10,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,付き合うのはおよしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.40,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.40,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕は...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.81,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'm his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.81,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕はあいつの兄弟なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:31.20,Default,woman,0,0,0,,R-Really? Well, I do beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:31.20,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,そ そうかい そりゃ悪いこと言ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.11,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.11,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.16,Default,cor,0,0,0,,No matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.16,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.24,Default,cor,0,0,0,,This is your favorite place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.24,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ここがお気に入りの場所なの?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.06,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.63,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You came here a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.63,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,よく来てたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.39,Default,av,0,0,0,,No. It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.39,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いや 初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.50,Default,av,0,0,0,,That day, Luce told me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.50,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あの日 ルーチェが言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.86,Default,av,0,0,0,,he wanted to go to the zoo someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.86,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,動物園に行ってみたいって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.47,Default,cor,0,0,0,,We can start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.47,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕たちはやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.11,Default,cor,0,0,0,,We'll start over together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.11,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,二人で生き直すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.42,Default,woman,0,0,0,,Mr. Corteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.42,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,コルテオさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.56,Default,woman,0,0,0,,You have a call from a man named Angelo Lagusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.56,通用720日文-ja,woman,0,0,0,,アンジェロ ラグーザって人から電話だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.68,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.68,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.06,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.06,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.06,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Come back at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.06,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,すぐに帰ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.61,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You need to save Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.61,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,アヴィリオを救ってやってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.21,Default,bar,0,0,0,,You sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.21,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ここに座れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.94,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Why did you try to kill Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.94,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,なぜネロを狙った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:12.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I don't recall doing anything to earn your hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:12.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺はお前に恨まれるようなことをした覚えはねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:19.89,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I wanted to save Avilio from this ridiculous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:19.89,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕はアヴィリオを救い出したかった こんなくだらないところから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.05,Default,cor,0,0,0,,With you gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.05,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,お前さえいなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.05,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.05,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.45,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Were you and Avilio working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.45,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,お前とアヴィリオはグルだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.85,Default,cor,0,0,0,,No. I did it all of my own initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.85,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,違う 全部僕が勝手にやったことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It was Avilio who got you out of the garage, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.78,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ガレージからお前を逃がしたのもアヴィリオだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.80,Default,cor,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.80,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.99,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,お前を波止場で見た者がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:39.70,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Someone saw you on the pier the day Avilio left for Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.70,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アヴィリオはシカゴへ発ったその日に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.54,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.54,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,そんなところ行ったこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:45.83,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Liar! You both went after Nero together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:45.83,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,嘘をつくな お前たちは二人でネロを狙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.08,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Avilio's in your way, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.08,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,あんたはアヴィリオが邪魔なんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.93,Default,cor,0,0,0,,He could steal your position as Nero's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.93,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ネロの右腕の座を奪われるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.53,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.53,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.55,Default,bar,0,0,0,,But, Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.55,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,しかしネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.30,Default,bar,0,0,0,,These two have always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.30,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,こいつらは昔からの...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.99,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.99,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前がやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:11.18,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:11.18,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なぜ 戻ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.80,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Ganzo said that you were in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.80,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ガンゾから君が危ないって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:20.38,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But even if he hadn't, it would end the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:20.38,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でも 連絡がなかったとしても同じことさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.29,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Either way, I'd end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.29,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,どの道 僕は...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:26.66,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You can use that gun to clear their suspicion of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:26.66,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その銃で アヴィリオの疑いも晴れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.29,Default,cor,0,0,0,,No one will get in your way after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.29,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,もう誰も 邪魔する奴はいない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.66,Default,av,0,0,0,,I am here to take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.66,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,復讐するためにここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.22,Default,av,0,0,0,,It's not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.22,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それは終わってない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.83,Default,cor,0,0,0,,It's been a crazy ride, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.83,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,なんだか 慌しかったなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.92,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,アヴィリオがこの町に戻ってきてから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.75,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Has it really only been three months since you came back to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.75,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,たった三ヶ月か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:58.95,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But I'm glad I got to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:58.95,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でも また会えて嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.48,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.48,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なんて
